Concorde White(CW)

White kitchens cabinets are sure to enhance the kitchen’s design radiating a classy and transitional setting. This Concorde White door style offers an adaptable option that adds originality and interest to any kitchen and will look equally stylish in modern or classic spaces.

DESCRIPTION:

With its white clean lines and unique edges, this snow frost door is certain to make an impact in any home.

    Specification

  • Door
    • Full overlay door with mortise and tenon construction
    • Solid wood door frames with ⅜” MDF center panel
    • Blumotion soft-close mechanism integrated in concealed six-way adjustable hinges
  • Drawer
    • 5-piece recessed panel drawer fronts
    • ⅝” solid birch drawer box with dovetail construction
    • Tandem plus Blumotion full extension concealed drawer runners
  • Box
    • Dovetail construction
    • ½” select birch plywood construction
    • ¾” adjustable shelves edge-banded in wood veneer natural finish
    • Base cabinet has 18” deep shelves
  • Finishing
    • Natural wood veneer finished interior
